This is a way to reduce binary size for VLC

2 parts.

1. VLCKit: plugins, disable linkage with external libraries. (***libavio???)

Modify 2 files:
    VLCKit/MobileVLCKit/MobileVLCKit.xcconfig
    VLCKit/MobileVLCKit/ImportedSources/vlc/extras/package/ios/build.sh
Details:
    https://wiki.videolan.org/Contrib_Status

2. ffmpeg disable most decoders, demux, parsers. disable all encoders

Modify 1 file:
    rules.mak in VLCKit/MobileVLCKit/ImportedSources/vlc/contrib/src/ffmpeg
Details:
    http://www.ffmpeg.org/ffmpeg-protocols.html
    http://www.ffmpeg.org/documentation.html
    http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_62a8419a01016exv.html